snippet.title: Böbl Trailer (NES)
snippet.description:
Free NES ROM download at https://morphcatgames.itch.io/bobl
- you're a bubble
- water is your friend, solid blocks kill you
- "rubber ducky jumps" only
   i.e., hold A to dive, then release and let buoyancy handle the rest

Made for NESdev competition 2019/20. You can check out the other competition entries here: https://neshomebrew.ca/contest19/

To play on PC or Mac, get an NES emulator!
( e.g., Nestopia http://nestopia.sourceforge.net/ )




Old (1.0) version available here:
https://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=35&t=19718
